{"tid":1801710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12.29 持伸縮警棍男遭10多人圍毆 途人大聲喝止","createTime":"2019-12-28T22:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T12:17:56.000Z","uid":49336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dc4fc3e83729bb0b357c0d6f223f294753359473","tid":1801710,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T22:56:52.000Z","msg":"旺角西洋菜南街與豉油街交界，凌晨零時許，一名手臂紋身持伸縮警棍男子，遭約10名男子持硬物及鐵棒毆打襲擊，事主不敵被圍毆受傷倒卧地上，途人見發生血案大聲喝止，逞兇者四散逃去，救護員趕至將傷者送院治理，現場留下一灘血迹，警員封鎖現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n據現場目擊者表示，傷者原本乘坐一輛寶馬私家車，落車後遭多人持硬物追打，事主逃跑至10多米外，被追至惡漢包圍狂毆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191229/60427888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F60427888&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=e115ca8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F60427888&h=43192617\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191229/60427888</a>"},{"pid":"e759501f27484b61efbf28f16e4206747c6bdeda","tid":1801710,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T22:57:37.000Z","msg":"「12.25」新城市左膠阻人救人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1797272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1797272</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A42vt1s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA42vt1s.gif&h=2da8f385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S73FReV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS73FReV.gif&h=781a6f26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3093b60559d17579673dfee1ec687991729c7ed","tid":1801710,"uid":225347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e759501f27484b61efbf28f16e4206747c6bdeda","tid":1801710,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"re